These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, jet-ski
City: liverpool, hamburg
There are 2 different favourite colors: light-blue, green
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: time-travel, animation
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, horse
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: orchid, amaryllis
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
2. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
3. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
5. the person who growsamaryllis is the person traveling to hamburg##1
6. the person who likes green is the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Beverage      | tea        | hot-chocolate |
| Transport          | jet-ski  | van     |
| City         | hamburg    | liverpool         |
| Color           | light-blue    | green |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel  | animation     |
| Pet           | horse      | chinchilla    |
| Flower         | amaryllis | orchid          |

