2 different pets are kept: goat, mouse
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, van
1. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the futuristic house##1
2. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person driving the van is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
4. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |
| House         | futuristic      | wooden       |
| Sport           | rugby | badminton |
| Beverage   | fanta      | tea        |
| City   | berlin         | hannover        |
| Food   | radish    | watermelon       |
| Pet           | mouse        | goat          |
| Transport     | van          | snowmobile    |

