.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-3-3::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, game
2 different games are played: whist, mah-jongg
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, rock-climbing
The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, teacher
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: scientific, comedy
There are 2 different favourite colors: blood-red, white
House: futuristic, tower
1. the tower house is on the left or right of the dancer##3
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3
3. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3
4. the futuristic house is on the left of the person playing whist##1
5. the game-smoker is on the right of the person who likes white##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |
| Cigar      | chaman | game  |
| Game          | mah-jongg   | whist   |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | puzzles   |
| Job           | dancer        | teacher   |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy      | scientific |
| Color         | white    | blood-red  |
| House     | futuristic       | tower      |

